<section class="partner-page">
  <div class="partner-shell">

    <div class="partner-card">
      <div class="partner-eyebrow">Partner With Rofo</div>
      <h1>Get in Front of Businesses Actively Looking for Space</h1>
      <p class="partner-lead">
        Rofo helps businesses discover office, retail, and industrial space in the right markets. Partner with Rofo to feature your building, market expertise, or local presence where tenants are actively searching.
      </p>
      <p class="partner-mini-note">
        Built for brokers, landlords, and local market professionals who want targeted visibility at the moment of tenant intent.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="partner-stack">

      <div class="partner-card">
        <div class="partner-eyebrow">Why Rofo</div>
        <p>
          Rofo is designed for discovery. Businesses use Rofo to explore markets, compare buildings, and learn before they commit. That creates an opportunity for brokers and landlords to appear earlier in the search process.
        </p>

        <div class="partner-grid-3">
          <div>
            <h3>High-intent audience</h3>
            <p>Reach businesses already looking for office, retail, or industrial space.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>Local market visibility</h3>
            <p>Show up on city pages and in relevant market content.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>Curated placement</h3>
            <p>Stand out in a cleaner, more focused environment than traditional listing platforms.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="partner-card">
        <div class="partner-eyebrow">Who It’s For</div>

        <div class="partner-grid-2">
          <div>
            <h3>For brokers</h3>
            <p>
              Be featured as a local market expert and connect with businesses exploring space in your city.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>For landlords</h3>
            <p>
              Showcase your building on relevant city pages and put your property in front of active searchers.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="partner-card">
        <div class="partner-eyebrow">Opportunities to partner</div>

        <div class="partner-grid-3">
          <div>
            <h3>Featured Buildings</h3>
            <p>Appear in prominent positions on city pages where tenants are actively exploring options.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>Local Expert Placement</h3>
            <p>Be featured as a tenant rep or market specialist in a specific city.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>Market Sponsorship</h3>
            <p>Own visibility in a market through premium placement and supporting presence across key pages.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="partner-card">
        <div class="partner-eyebrow">Flexible Participation</div>
        <p>
          Rofo offers straightforward opportunities based on market, visibility, and placement type. That can include featured positions, local expert presence, and broader market sponsorships.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="partner-card">
        <div class="partner-eyebrow">Get in Touch</div>
        <p>
          Tell us your market, your role, and what you’d like to feature.
        </p>

        <form action="https://formspree.io/f/mojpbqre" method="POST" class="partner-form">
          <input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="New Rofo Partner Inquiry">

          <div class="partner-form-grid">
            <div>
              <label for="partner-name">Name</label>
              <input id="partner-name" type="text" name="name" required>
            </div>
            <div>
              <label for="partner-company">Company</label>
              <input id="partner-company" type="text" name="company">
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="partner-form-grid">
            <div>
              <label for="partner-email">Email</label>
              <input id="partner-email" type="email" name="email" required>
            </div>
            <div>
              <label for="partner-role">Role</label>
              <select id="partner-role" name="role">
                <option value="Broker">Broker</option>
                <option value="Landlord">Landlord</option>
                <option value="Other">Other</option>
              </select>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="partner-form-grid">
            <div>
              <label for="partner-market">Market</label>
              <input id="partner-market" type="text" name="market" placeholder="e.g. San Francisco">
            </div>
            <div>
              <label for="partner-interest">Interest</label>
              <select id="partner-interest" name="interest">
                <option value="Featured Building">Featured Building</option>
                <option value="Local Expert Placement">Local Expert Placement</option>
                <option value="Market Sponsorship">Market Sponsorship</option>
                <option value="General Partnership Inquiry">General Partnership Inquiry</option>
              </select>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <label for="partner-message">Message</label>
            <textarea id="partner-message" name="message" placeholder="Tell us what you're interested in"></textarea>
          </div>

          <div>
            <button class="btn-primary" type="submit">Submit Inquiry</button>
          </div>
        </form>

        
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>